{"tid":604778,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"童子尿蛋防中暑 檔販：連湯喝更佳","createTime":"2018-03-25T05:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T09:45:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":136,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"1c93efe9550d4ee0f75d73ea3dc50c38835c9c49","tid":604778,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:22:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180325/20342266\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180325%2F20342266&d=rnLJWTJRiABdN9x9mvKqb4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=66790e15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180325%2F20342266&h=913b7b3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180325/20342266</a><br />\n<br />\n童子尿蛋防中暑<br />\n檔販：連湯喝更佳<br />\n<br />\n兩岸要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180325/large/25cb5p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180325%2Flarge%2F25cb5p.jpg&h=2f8946c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n檔主將童子尿倒入雞蛋中。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這是春天的味道。踏入3月，浙江東陽市面就會傳來陣陣「飄香」，一股尿餲味瀰漫四周，原來當地流行在3月吃童子尿蛋，街邊許多攤檔正不停澆尿煮蛋叫賣鑊中即時蒸起一陣陣「尿煙」。有當地檔販說，吃了童尿蛋的人，夏天不容易中暑和犯睏，而且喝下「湯」效果更好。<br />\n<br />\n童子尿煮蛋，不僅是當地傳統美食，更在2008年獲選為當地非物質文化遺產。有賣童子尿蛋的店家豪言，一天能賣上300、400隻蛋。不過有外地人買來一試後，即撒手擰頭、皺起眉毛直呼「不吃了不吃了！味道太重！」<br />\n<br />\n而當地檔販製作童子尿蛋最重要的原料是尿，一般採用當地小學三年級或以下的健康男孩尿，店家會一般在幼兒園或小學收集男孩尿液。街頭販賣的是無添加的尿蛋，味道除了來自雞蛋本身，就都是尿的精華。<br />\n<br />\n梨視頻"},{"pid":"8d292b256e9cf8751ba249c39452b1cbc228e738","tid":604778,"uid":116836,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:23:55.000Z","msg":"今日飲左未"},{"pid":"28ebda997855212eabcfb1fe0425b74c33ad526f","tid":604778,"uid":5715,"like":135,"dislike":0,"score":135,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:24:29.000Z","msg":"隨時係麻甩佬啲尿扮童子尿， 而且尿煮蛋都好食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888b176478c2adb5824752011912c6b56d7adf82","tid":604778,"uid":77057,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"28ebda997855212eabcfb1fe0425b74c33ad526f","tid":604778,"uid":5715,"like":135,"dislike":0,"score":135,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:24:29.000Z","msg":"隨時係麻甩佬啲尿扮童子尿， 而且尿煮蛋都好食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:25:58.000Z","msg":"仲有狗尿"},{"pid":"f82ce5aa7c8397ff0e0bd4c766dd59f5f309899a","tid":604778,"uid":68220,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:26:11.000Z","msg":"唔明尿有咩好飲<br />\n無營養同臭嘅水<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4f8e7fbc767ef351da640df9a42282da1256ad","tid":604778,"uid":140802,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:27:13.000Z","msg":"點解要童子先有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501e09a6b5e15d8fc317c0dc906e36e0e78cb07f","tid":604778,"uid":1248,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:30:08.000Z","msg":"中國人最鍾意將放得入口既野吹到天花龍鳳"},{"pid":"2a717a03430ed73258da8b5cb14f97cb4a5b8fbf","tid":604778,"uid":125079,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:31:22.000Z","msg":"民智未開"},{"pid":"142067e86fee3ef9db66eebe269bd2d0e03536e3","tid":604778,"uid":33091,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:31:54.000Z","msg":"非物質文化遺產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b4c412fa93686c0598653d4b4504ef4998f0d6","tid":604778,"uid":46943,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"501e09a6b5e15d8fc317c0dc906e36e0e78cb07f","tid":604778,"uid":1248,"like":39,"dislik